               <p>On the 24th of September as I was getting my pots in <placeName id="t17781021-10-crimeloc57">Beach-lane</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17781021-10-crimeloc57" type="placeName" value="Beach-lane"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17781021-10-crimeloc57" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17781021-10-off55 t17781021-10-crimeloc57"></join>, I went into a house; I put some pots on the bottom of the stairs, and went up to a lodger; when I came down I missed one of my pots; I saw the prisoner going out, I followed her and found the pot under her cloak; she said she took it to get some water.</p>
               <p>(
               <persName id="t17781021-10-person128">
                  John
                   Towers
               <interp inst="t17781021-10-person128" type="surname" value="Towers"></interp>
